VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT java\.net\.HttpURLConnection
WHEN EXPR MISSING:https://|HttpsURLConnection|SSLContext|TrustManager|HSTS && MISSING:localhost|127\.0\.0\.1|test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of the java.net.HttpURLConnection package, which may expose applications to insecure HTTP connections.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Package: java.net.HttpURLConnection.
